{"tid":1757444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（抵制TVB）12月簽約死線漸近 大家要keep住做任呀！是晚商戶Osim","createTime":"2019-11-26T13:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T17:22:07.000Z","uid":75759,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c11796f5653ab153574460090e714a62cc8bf336","tid":1757444,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:45:01.000Z","msg":"經過各位巴絲日日努力幫手洗版<br />\nCCTVB<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">僅餘嘅</span></strong>廣告商都<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">洗得七七八八</span></strong>啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋就打算轉一轉行動方針<br />\ntarget啲宜家冇廣告但往年<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">會簽定下一年廣告嘅大客</span></strong><br />\n好言相勸佢哋同TVB割蓆 等我哋可以用銀紙懲罰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你尊重我時我哋一定支持你<br />\n相反你俾錢假新聞機器造假老屈我哋啦喎<br />\n咪等荷蘭叻之流幫襯囉 不過等到幾時先等到就唔知啦<br />\n你睇吓華星冰室上港台個慘慘豬樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kty9R6x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkty9R6x.gif&h=f07f3cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是晚勸誡@26 Nov 2019 <br />\nOsim<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/HKOSIM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FHKOSIM%2F&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=e144fe63\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/HKOSIM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGXyzkz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGXyzkz.jpg&h=bb1bc9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪話樓豬唔教精你啦，宜家民心所向喺邊大家都有眼睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未計中小學手足我地都疊馬過班五毛藍絲多多聲啦！在商言商，有咩公司仲會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冒俾全香港人放棄個風險</span></strong>死攬每分每秒都無所不用其極地唱衰香港人嘅假新聞機器CCTVB？Osim你自己諗啦！<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色經濟圈，等緊你加入呀！</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">割蓆唔洗錢，仲有免費宣傳效果，你唔係仲LD同落下年TVB廣告呀？</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n專業小知識：LD點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">廣告商2018年年尾預繳咗錢，於2019年係CCTVB播廣告。點知間廣告商預繳咗嘅錢係2019年用唔晒，想將預繳咗嘅錢帶落2020年用，咁就為之LD啦！</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拒廣告、冇煩惱！</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃圈捧、客無窮！<br />\n黃色經濟圈 又點少得你呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【勸諫廣告商任務流程】<br />\n1.俾<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">慘慘</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span></strong>俾嬲)<br />\n2.<del>唐三藏上身</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">留言</span></strong>勸諫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0oLz3e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oLz3e3.jpg&h=607da64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請用幾秒去俾慘慘、留言、推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">每日阻你一分鐘，咁都唔做對唔住前線巴絲呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請用新template，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勸誡夜</span></strong>專用：<br />\n<br />\n無綫新聞，出賣港人... 貴公司現無TVB廣告，我甚欣賞；若今年用盡餘下廣告預算，我亦理解。<br />\n我只誠盼 貴公司承諾不會LD，不會簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約及不會再以無綫藝人代言。<br />\n反之， 貴公司可能將被網民列入「永久抵制名單」， 恕本人只好永遠罷買，並呼籲朋友一同罷買。(暫時抵制名單: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JSJaQK&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=cf2698ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2JSJaQK</a>)<br />\n<br />\n記住同埋幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7RxRPAh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7RxRPAh.jpg&h=8314617b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/7RxRPAh.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7RxRPAh.jpg&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=c55d11dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/7RxRPAh.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n記得bookmark: TVB廣告客戶名單！！ <br />\n消費前諗清楚 👇<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=c978d19b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a><br />\n－－－－－－－ <br />\n請即follow: <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=f0c26222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG 綜合狙擊頻道(已復活，TVB狗係咪好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />): <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=fed95210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 繼續狙擊頻道(新channel，請follow): <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb2&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=948bd61b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb2</a><br />\nTG CCTVB記者實時位置狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/nomoretvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnomoretvb&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=aea26583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nomoretvb</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">割</span></span></strong>比落訂強<br />\n與<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>負累</strong></span></span>割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d6e77120a21b8bd87874767df7c0de8fdd0462","tid":1757444,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:48:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17f94126552b92815ded28e53e71fffed856a1fd","tid":1757444,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"恥與為伍"},{"pid":"50534aa6ae7f70647b243c33d16b4fcd8b90d957","tid":1757444,"uid":299611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dccfc9b549e902c3cf794901918d95c37656bc","tid":1757444,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635cc67f35d4852888e9cf4054e9b8ddcff63749","tid":1757444,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d8ae0f11693516ed31baa32ecb45a77346e668","tid":1757444,"uid":210956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:58:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0c8a4f5f46e97aa2acfd2a0f48506e5bfd99a23a","tid":1757444,"uid":210956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4152792a22